          alt="Kristen Ross, LPC"
          width="80"
          height="80"
          class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-primary mb-2">
            About Kristen Ross, LPC
          </h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Kristen Ross is a Licensed Professional Counselor and founder of Laurel Tree Counseling. With over 14 years of experience, she specializes in holistic approaches to mental health that integrate mind, body, and spirit. Her background includes certification in complementary medicine and wellness, and she leads a collaborative team of counselors and nutrition specialists.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Related Posts -->
